{"tid":738704,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"科技網站：陸版iPhone屏蔽「中華民國國旗」　傳訊會當機閃退","createTime":"2018-07-11T17:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T16:28:48.000Z","uid":29625,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3502af5a0872d93d32d719856a35d15716a287f","tid":738704,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"科技中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n近日有民眾在中國大陸使用iPhone，結果發現中華民國國旗的表情符號不僅無法正常顯示，還會造成App當機閃退。有國外安全性研究員推測，蘋果可能為了向中共示好，在iOS系統「屏蔽」青天白日滿地紅旗幟，但蘋果公司至今尚未對外回應。<br />\n<br />\n根據國外科技網站The Wired、CNET、ZDNet等報導，曾在美國國家安全局（NSA）工作的華德爾日前發現，只要台灣籍友人在中國大陸境內使用iPhone，或把iPhone地區設為中國，中華民國的表情符號便無法顯示，還會在接收訊息時顯示符號遺失。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，華德爾反覆測試後，發現蘋果公司明顯有在iOS系統新增某些程式碼，目的是讓中國境內的iPhone無法顯示中華民國國旗，但這些刻意新增的程式碼卻存在一項「無心的錯誤」（unintentional bug），導致App閃退當機；而且早自2017年初開始，iOS就已包含相關審查機制。<br />\n<br />\n▲▼科技網站：陸版iPhone屏蔽「中華民國國旗」　傳訊會當機閃退。（圖／記者柯沛辰攝）<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，青天白日滿地紅在中國大陸境內的iPhone上消失，只是蘋果公司向中共做出的數項讓步之一；因為蘋果公司先前曾把中國用戶的資料移往中國大陸境內的伺服器，還曾在中國App Store移除能避開中國審查機制的虛擬私有網路（VPN）。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果在最新發布的iOS 11.4.1作業系統更新說明文件中指出，其中一項安全性更新與表情符號有關，原因是在某些設定環境下處理一個表情符號，可能造成阻斷服務（denial of service）；雖然更新內容並未言明是何種問題，但外界懷疑正是指中華民國國旗導致的當機閃退。<br />\n<br />\n《中央社》報導指出，他們記者11日致電向蘋果公司查證，但至今未取得回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180711/1210747.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180711%2F1210747.htm&d=oh7JcOOpwMC6L4TJ8iaMlF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f279ebfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180711/1210747.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e2901a82e9b179faa04554315c56c553a855dac3","tid":738704,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:05:30.000Z","msg":"有鬼佬研究發現，會crash係因為iOS有段叫removeEmoji嘅code<br />\n只要地區set做CN再render台灣國旗就會出事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://objective-see.com/blog/blog_0x34.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobjective-see.com%2Fblog%2Fblog_0x34.html&d=oh7JcOOpwMC6L4TJ8iaMlF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2ec73a48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://objective-see.com/blog/blog_0x34.html</a><br />\n<br />\n而上年已經有人發現中國地區係無咗青天白日滿地紅旗emoji<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/010034_160bff672509c9b1b1cc272b0e6ae1a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F010034_160bff672509c9b1b1cc272b0e6ae1a2.png&h=8f9c97dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b4a9ffe81e7164320934eca5391c1bd61e084d0","tid":738704,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"屌 開錯區 應該開去CC台"},{"pid":"313c27c6047ecf8d16eeefd215219d8e1f78faf0","tid":738704,"uid":149902,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f63c71f4986d8506bc1445a20778af9c8f1c313a","tid":738704,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808c35b0e8bb838e42e0df6a78fd76d780795cfc","tid":738704,"uid":61271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"支那係世界上最應該消失既國家"},{"pid":"b7ba93f216283d42389f2c783820ddc58929785b","tid":738704,"uid":30468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"用緊IPhone 6s Plus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係時候換返Android啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95e94dca33dd8afcf48e0d24741d1f52f6811e2","tid":738704,"uid":7886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"Ifan 都會「屏蔽」呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a195e52777e231c377bf19fd19c3c5adff3763","tid":738704,"uid":35542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T18:24:13.000Z","msg":"睇返原文啦，唔好信晒中文翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原文都無講過事主有返過大陸，佢係region set做美國，語言第一set做英文第二set做繁體中文都中招呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於Apple係咪奶共，你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec35ce3e0e3d06313ba72b8942d9c8bab07b4fb5","tid":738704,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"睇原文 11.4 fix左 <br />\n但咁明顯既&quot;bug&quot;<br />\n仲要唔係中國境內限定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f43cf6fec18d4071e6ec3bedb3a11897acc9d30","tid":738704,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"不如一打中國或國旗就出中國2025<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f49c684bbc8ff37bc60658e8ced1f867e81013","tid":738704,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"又中國不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83bc68a2c1e1712aac3a6cbd1b7d34ab420637c","tid":738704,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"🇹🇼"},{"pid":"416cb398957afb6372a0909be249f068a2a6fed5","tid":738704,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"整埋呢啲無謂 filter 唔好叫蘋果喇<br />\n叫高登啦"}]}